CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Propanc Biopharma Inc is a development-stage healthcare company. It focuses on developing new cancer treatments for patients suffering from pancreatic, ovarian, and colorectal cancer. The company develops a rational, composite formulation of the anti-cancer compound, which together exert a number of effects designed to control or prevent tumors from recurring and spreading through the body. Its product, PRP, is a variation upon its novel formulation and involves proenzymes, the inactive precursors of enzymes.
